                    : Schedule annual wellness exams with your veterinarian to monitor your cat's health, administer vaccinations, and address any concerns or health issues.
                </p>
                    
                </li>
                <li> <p><span>Enrichment and Play</span>
                    : Provide opportunities for your cat to engage in mental and physical stimulation through interactive toys, scratching posts, and play sessions. Cats need both mental and physical exercise to stay happy and healthy.</p>
